---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Affiliate Disclosure - Imperial Picks" description="Read the Affiliate Disclosure for Imperial Picks (https://imperialpicks.in). Learn how we use affiliate links and how we maintain 100% independent and honest reviews.">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="relative bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Background Patterns -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <!-- Header Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-16 pb-10 sm:pt-20 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          Affiliate Disclosure
        </h1>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
          <span>Website URL: <a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a></span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline text-slate-300">•</span>
          <span>Last Updated: June 10, 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclosure Content -->
    <section class="relative py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-xs space-y-8">
          
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Transparency and trust form the foundation of Imperial Picks. In compliance with advertising guidelines and consumer protection standards, we want to disclose that this website (<a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a>) contains affiliate links. This means we may receive commissions when you click on links and buy featured software packages.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              1. What is an Affiliate Link?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              An affiliate link is a tracking URL provided by software networks or vendor platforms. When you click one of these outbound links on our site and complete a purchase or sign up for a subscription plan, a tracking cookie registers that you visited from Imperial Picks. The vendor then pays us a small referral commission. This occurs at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>—in fact, affiliate partnerships sometimes grant us access to discount promo codes that lower your price.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              2. Commitment to Editorial Independence
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our highest priority is delivering honest curation, comparison write-ups, and calculators to our visitors. Affiliate relationships do not compromise our reviews:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              <li>
                <strong>No Bias:</strong> We review the features, speeds, pros, and cons of tools objectively. If a popular tool has bugs or is overpriced, we state so clearly, regardless of commission rates.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Organic Recommendations:</strong> We list many products that have no affiliate program simply because they represent top-tier options in their category.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Rankings Integrity:</strong> Community voting on our directory remains organic. Creators cannot buy vote placements, and upvoting metrics are driven purely by users.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              3. Why Do We Use Affiliate Links?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Operating a highly detailed directory with real-time interactive ROI calculators, guides, and upvote infrastructures requires ongoing hosting, licensing, and writing overhead. Rather than placing our content behind restrictive paywalls, charging subscription fees, or showing intrusive, distracting display ads, we use affiliate commissions to keep Imperial Picks completely free for the creator community.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              4. Our Trust Promise
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We value the relationship we build with developers, startup founders, and marketers. We only review and recommend products we believe add true value to your digital workflows. If we suggest a product, it is because we have researched its capabilities, analyzed consumer feedback, or tested it in-house.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Details -->
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Partner & Disclosure Questions</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              If you have any questions, wish to know more about our partnerships, or want to discuss a listing, contact our relationships manager at:
              <a href="mailto:imperialpicks00@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 font-bold hover:underline ml-1">
                imperialpicks00@gmail.com
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
